      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate order-of-accuracy verification on canonical rotating-flow benchmarks at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Solver order-of-accuracy verified against the Taylor–Green vortex and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Second-order spatial convergence confirmed. Results consistent with published ANSYS verification documentation."
    },
