      "rationale": "Inlet flow rates (2–8 L/min) and rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM) match FDA experimental protocol. Fluid temperature and hematocrit controlled to ±2% of target. Boundary condition fidelity confirmed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
