      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis power-law constants) acknowledged but not formally quantified at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for rotating blood-contacting devices. Hemolysis power-law exponents from Giersiepen et al. Model form uncertainty noted but not required to be formally bounded at MRL 2."
